## A Maven project usually has a standard directory structure
like src/main/java for source code and src/test/java for tests. 
Maven can generate this using the quickstart archetype command. 

- command to create project - 

mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.example -DartifactId=CreateMavenProject -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart -DinteractiveMode=false
